               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>The words sälam and Ṣadǝqan (ʾo-Ṣadǝqan) throughout the text and the word ʾamḫa on fol. 4v. Elements of the punctuation signs.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
