                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- In the Ms., the group of Ṣadǝqan to whom the text is dedicated is in not named; however, the text is the same as the "Mälkǝʾa Ṣadǝqan [zä-Baräknaha]" in<ref type="mss" corresp="ESdsm017">DSM-017</ref>, fols. 19ra-22va. In<ref type="mss" corresp="ESmy026">MY-026</ref>b the beginning strophes (= strophes nos. 1-23 in<ref type="mss" corresp="ESdsm017">DSM-017</ref>) are missing.</note>
                     <note>- Fols. 1r-1v, 4r-6v are blank but ruled.</note>
                  </msItem>
